<plot>Documentary questioning the reliability and reasonableness of the Danish police investigating themselves when accidents happen during arrests. Jonna Ørskov from Løgstør in Northen Jutland and Marianne Schou from Copenhagen tell how their sons encounter with the police had fatal consequences. Jonna's son died in the custody of the police. Marianne's son is 100% handicapped after his arrest.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?629412</url></doc>
